      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Monster Mash",
        "Client": "Citadel Ecology Researcher",
        "Description": "Someone\u0027s reported seeing the\r\nThree Lords at the Citadel. All\r\nof them! We have no record\r\nof them meeting before, but\r\na brawl between these beasts\r\ncould devastate the entire region.\r\nYou know what to do, Hunter!",
